 Insight ID: INS001
 Insight Type: Location
 Target Category: Whitefield
 Condition: If user wants high rental income near IT corridors
 Recommendation: Invest in 2BHK apartments in Whitefield priced between 80L–1.2Cr
 Reasoning: Whitefield hosts ITPL and major tech parks driving consistent tenant demand from IT professionals. Vacancy
 rates remain below 5% year-round.
 Expected Outcome: Stable rental income with 4–5% annual yield and 8–10% capital appreciation
 Risk Level: Low
 Confidence Level: High

