Insight ID: INS007
Insight Type: Property Type
Target Category: Plot
Condition: If user wants maximum flexibility and long-term land value growth
Recommendation: Acquire BMRDA or BBMP-approved plots in KR Puram or Yelahanka below 50L
Reasoning: Plots provide construction flexibility, attract lower GST, and appreciate faster in growth corridors. Land scarcity
in Bangalore ensures floor-level pricing support.
Expected Outcome: High appreciation of 15–25% over 5–7 years with optional self-construction upside
Risk Level: Medium
Confidence Level: Medium

