Insight ID: INS014
Insight Type: Strategy
Target Category: Rental Focus
Condition: If user wants immediate and consistent monthly rental cash flow
Recommendation: Buy furnished 2BHK apartments near IT parks in Whitefield or Electronic City and list on corporate lease
Reasoning: Corporate leases offer rent 20–30% above market with 11-month lock-ins, reducing vacancy risk. IT
professional demand ensures rapid tenant placement.
Expected Outcome: Net rental yield of 4–5% annually with near-zero vacancy in peak IT hiring cycles
Risk Level: Low
Confidence Level: High

Insight ID: INS015
